    rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FOODON_03450013>.
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FOODON_03450026> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Cooked with sufficient fat or oil to coat and moisten the food being prepared, but not cooked in enough fat or oil to immerse the food."@en;
    <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "http://www.langual.org/langual_thesaurus.asp?termid=G0026";
