<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FOODON_03450020> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Cooking in a moderate amount of liquid at just below the boiling point."@en;
    <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "http://www.langual.org/langual_thesaurus.asp?termid=G0020";
